{"tid":2059625,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【突發】署理副廣播處長陳敏娟因健康理由請辭　9月起離任","createTime":"2020-06-11T05:14:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T05:14:17.000Z","uid":184643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"af342de6df9a81db1508b71ba281c06bf5cc6462","tid":2059625,"uid":184643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T05:14:17.000Z","msg":"署理副廣播處長陳敏娟辭職，9月1日離任。<br />\n<br />\n香港電台機構傳訊組總監伍曼儀表示，陳敏娟早上在港台高層會議上透露，因為健康理由，6月1日向廣播處長提出請辭。<br />\n<br />\n現年58歲的陳敏娟，在港台任職超過30年，港台感謝陳敏娟多年以來的服務及貢獻。<br />\n<br />\n至於陳敏娟辭職後的工作安排，伍曼儀表示，港台會因應運作需要及根據公務員事務規例，安排合適人員署任副廣播處長（節目）的職位。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1531434-20200611.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1531434-20200611.htm&d=zXAIbGZ2Qohx5%2Bb7%2FAbjRFFFw%2Fpr%2F0Xu32W9HouEUHQ%3D&h=bb745dcd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1531434-20200611.htm&h=a49d8cc1\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1531434-20200611.htm</a>"}]}